hotelDesc.overview:
Discover Luxury at NewCZ Haeundae Residence in Busan

Welcome to NewCZ Haeundae Residence, a stunning 4-star hotel that is set to redefine luxury accommodation in the vibrant city of Busan, South Korea. Opened in 2024, this modern establishment boasts a prime location, offering guests easy access to the picturesque Haeundae Beach and the bustling local attractions. With a total of 90 elegantly designed rooms, NewCZ Haeundae Residence combines contemporary aesthetics with comfort, ensuring a memorable stay for every traveler. Guests can enjoy a seamless check-in experience starting from 4:00 PM, allowing ample time to settle in and unwind before exploring the local culture. The check-out time is set until 11:00 AM, providing a leisurely morning to savor the hotel’s amenities. Families will appreciate the hotel's child policy, which allows children between the ages of 6 to 7 to stay free of charge, making it an ideal destination for family vacations. At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, every detail is curated to enhance your experience, ensuring that your stay in Busan is nothing short of extraordinary.

Relax and Unwind at NewCZ Haeundae Residence's Hot Tub Haven

At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, guests are invited to indulge in a serene escape with the luxurious hot tub facilities that promise to elevate your stay. Nestled within the hotel, this inviting hot tub area offers a tranquil oasis where you can soak away the stresses of the day. Surrounded by elegant decor and soothing ambiance, the hot tub provides a perfect setting for relaxation, whether you're unwinding after a day of exploring Busan's vibrant attractions or simply enjoying a moment of peace. The hot tub experience at NewCZ Haeundae Residence is designed for comfort and rejuvenation. Imagine sinking into warm, bubbling waters while enjoying stunning views of the surrounding cityscape or the gentle sounds of nature. This facility is not just about relaxation; it’s a social hub where guests can connect, share stories, and make lasting memories. Whether you're traveling solo, as a couple, or with family, the hot tub at NewCZ Haeundae Residence is the perfect spot to recharge and enjoy the finer things in life.

Unmatched Sports Facilities at NewCZ Haeundae Residence

At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, sports enthusiasts and leisure seekers alike will find a haven of activity and relaxation. The centerpiece of our sports facilities is the stunning indoor pool, where guests can enjoy a refreshing swim year-round. Surrounded by modern decor and ample natural light, the pool area offers a serene escape for those looking to unwind after a day of exploration or to maintain their fitness routine. Whether you prefer a leisurely dip or a vigorous swim, our indoor pool caters to all preferences, ensuring a rejuvenating experience. In addition to the indoor pool, the NewCZ Haeundae Residence boasts direct access to the pristine Haeundae Beach, a renowned destination for sunbathers and water sports enthusiasts. Here, guests can engage in a variety of beach activities, from beach volleyball to paddleboarding, all while soaking up the sun and enjoying the breathtaking views of the coastline. With the perfect blend of indoor and outdoor sports facilities, NewCZ Haeundae Residence invites you to stay active and embrace the vibrant lifestyle of Busan.

Convenience at Your Fingertips: NewCZ Haeundae Residence Facilities

At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, convenience is a top priority, ensuring that every guest enjoys a seamless and stress-free stay. The hotel offers complimentary Wi-Fi in all rooms, allowing you to stay connected with loved ones or catch up on work while enjoying the comforts of your personal space. Additionally, the public areas are equipped with Wi-Fi, making it easy to share your travel experiences on social media or simply browse the internet while relaxing in the common spaces. For those who appreciate efficiency, the express check-in and check-out service at NewCZ Haeundae Residence is designed to save you valuable time, allowing you to focus on what truly matters during your trip. Furthermore, the luggage storage facility provides a convenient solution for guests who wish to explore the vibrant surroundings without the burden of their bags. Whether you arrive early or depart late, you can rest assured that your belongings are safe, giving you the freedom to fully immerse yourself in the beauty of Busan.

Convenient Transport Facilities at NewCZ Haeundae Residence

At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, guests can enjoy the convenience of onsite transport facilities designed to enhance their stay in the vibrant city of Busan. The hotel boasts a spacious car park, allowing visitors to easily self-park their vehicles without the hassle of searching for street parking. This feature not only provides peace of mind but also ensures that guests have quick and easy access to their cars whenever they need them. One of the standout aspects of the transport facilities at NewCZ Haeundae Residence is that the car park is free of charge for all guests. This thoughtful amenity allows travelers to save on parking expenses, making it a budget-friendly option for those exploring the beautiful Haeundae area. Whether you're planning a day at the beach or a visit to local attractions, having a vehicle conveniently parked onsite makes it easy to embark on your adventures with ease.

Exceptional Room Facilities at NewCZ Haeundae Residence

Experience unparalleled comfort and convenience at NewCZ Haeundae Residence, where each room is thoughtfully designed to cater to your every need. Enjoy the perfect climate with air conditioning that ensures a refreshing atmosphere, allowing you to unwind after a day of exploring the vibrant city of Busan. Each room is equipped with a state-of-the-art television featuring satellite and cable channels, providing endless entertainment options right at your fingertips. For your convenience, a hair dryer is also available, ensuring you look your best before heading out to enjoy the local attractions. Indulge in the comforts of home with a separate living room that offers ample space to relax or entertain guests. Sip on freshly brewed coffee or tea from your in-room coffee/tea maker, or savor the complimentary bottled water provided for your hydration needs. A refrigerator is also included, perfect for storing snacks and beverages during your stay. To enhance your experience, a selection of quality toiletries is provided, ensuring you feel pampered throughout your visit. At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, every detail is curated to create a serene and enjoyable retreat for your stay in Busan.





Luxurious Room Offerings at NewCZ Haeundae Residence

At NewCZ Haeundae Residence, guests are invited to indulge in a selection of exquisitely designed rooms that cater to diverse preferences and needs. The Deluxe Double City View room, spanning 26 square meters, offers a cozy retreat with a plush double bed, perfect for couples seeking a romantic getaway. For families or groups, the Deluxe Family City View room provides more space at 33 square meters, featuring either a Japanese futon or a double bed, ensuring a comfortable stay for everyone. The Deluxe Family Twin Room, larger at 36 square meters, is ideal for those needing versatile sleeping arrangements, with options for a queen bed or a single bed, making it a perfect choice for families or friends traveling together. For those desiring a more opulent experience, the Royal Suites are the epitome of luxury, each encompassing a generous 92 square meters. Guests can choose between the Royal Suite, Royal Suite Ocean, or the Royal Suite with Partial Ocean View, all featuring two double beds that provide ample space for relaxation. The Panorama Suites elevate this experience further, with stunning layouts of 125 square meters and options for ocean views, accommodating both families and larger groups with their combination of Japanese futons and double beds. Finally, the Panorama Suite Pent Full Ocean, at 158 square meters, offers an unparalleled experience of space and comfort, perfect for those who wish to immerse themselves in the breathtaking views of the ocean. Booking these elegant accommodations through otaA not only guarantees you the best prices available but also ensures a hassle-free experience from start to finish. Enjoy the convenience of securing your ideal room with just a few clicks, allowing you to focus on what truly matters—creating unforgettable memories during your stay at NewCZ Haeundae Residence.

Discover the Vibrant Charm of Haeundae-gu, Busan

Nestled along the stunning coastline of Busan, Haeundae-gu is a vibrant district that effortlessly blends natural beauty with urban excitement. Known for its picturesque sandy beaches, Haeundae Beach is the crown jewel of the area, attracting locals and tourists alike with its soft golden sands and crystal-clear waters. As the sun rises, the beach comes alive with joggers, families, and sunbathers, while in the evenings, the vibrant nightlife spills onto the shores with beach bars and restaurants offering delicious local cuisine and refreshing drinks. The iconic Busan Aquarium, located at the edge of the beach, provides an engaging experience for families, showcasing diverse marine life from the depths of the ocean. Beyond the beach, Haeundae-gu is rich in cultural experiences and attractions. The bustling streets are lined with trendy cafes, boutique shops, and lively markets, where visitors can sample traditional Korean street food and shop for unique souvenirs. Just a short distance away, the serene Dongbaek Island offers a peaceful retreat with scenic walking paths, beautiful gardens, and breathtaking views of the coastline. For those interested in history and culture, the nearby Haedong Yonggungsa Temple, perched on a cliff overlooking the sea, provides a stunning backdrop for reflection and exploration. Haeundae-gu is not just a destination; it’s an experience that captures the essence of Busan’s coastal charm, making it an unforgettable place to visit.
